TITLE	Native 30S ribosomal subunit from S. solfataricus
DESCRIPTION	Native purification of the 30S ribosomal subunit using native conditions through the entire purification.  Samples were purified using a combination of ultra-centrifugation and gel-filtration chromatography.  Chromatography steps were monitored by multi-angle laser light scattering to determine the absolute molecular weight and monodispersity of the sample.
